description:
After Sonic traumatizes Robotnik one day, Robotnik tells Sleet and Dingo why he hates music so much. And the reason is one that nobody would have expected...
Support me and my art by joining my patreon www.patreon.com/Tamers12345 If I get enough support I might be able to even get Jaleel White(Sonic's VA) or one of the Jonas Brothers to guest star in a video one day.
